    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293640/extras/124ed21f938237374c5fb89032f6335f.poster.avif?t=1771896452\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293640/extras/124ed21f938237374c5fb89032f6335f.webm?t=1771896452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293640/extras/124ed21f938237374c5fb89032f6335f.mp4?t=1771896452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>剧情驱动</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演Evo，一个生活在衰败未来城市中的无业孤独者。你的治疗师为你安排了与Brunilda的约会，不久后你就发现她的生命处于危险之中。你是唯一能帮助她的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293640/extras/9cfe8858c7de34183148f19018ba31b5.poster.avif?t=1771896452\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293640/extras/9cfe8858c7de34183148f19018ba31b5.webm?t=1771896452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293640/extras/9cfe8858c7de34183148f19018ba31b5.mp4?t=1771896452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>现代第三人称射击战斗。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与负面特工对抗，这些恐吓Brunilda和她家人的电子生物大军。它们的起源仍是个谜，但有人推测它们与外星种族有关联。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293640/extras/141168402f76abc18fdc3ab0325be86a.poster.avif?t=1771896452\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293640/extras/141168402f76abc18fdc3ab0325be86a.webm?t=1771896452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293640/extras/141168402f76abc18fdc3ab0325be86a.mp4?t=1771896452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>拥抱奇异。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超现实事件、噩梦般的幻觉和扭曲的角色将带你踏上一段氛围紧张的刺激旅程。随着你逐渐陷入未知命运，世界中的传说和背景故事将逐渐揭露。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293640/extras/08eebf4c0c7b71d3fbb5354ec75d9263.poster.avif?t=1771896452\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293640/extras/08eebf4c0c7b71d3fbb5354ec75d9263.webm?t=1771896452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293640/extras/08eebf4c0c7b71d3fbb5354ec75d9263.mp4?t=1771896452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索一座垂死的城市。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >半开放世界设计让你可以驾车穿梭于建筑物和城市各区域之间。如果想避开游荡在街上的暴徒和杀戮机器，可以使用速度隧道快速穿越世界。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>附加详情：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>升级系统 - </strong>收集升级节点，在世界各处的升级工作台上强化你的武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>隐藏谜题 </strong>– 额外的隐藏谜题层将引导你前往秘密区域，获取叙事线索和令人不安的记忆。就像寻宝游戏一样，这些谜题可能遍布整个游戏世界，通常需要高度专注才能解开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>交互式环境 -</strong> 迷你游戏和设备使用使每个关卡保持新鲜感和趣味性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>备忘录和物品栏系统</strong> – 收集备忘录、必要设备和关键物品来辅助你的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>氛围音效与配音</strong> – 沉浸在令人毛骨悚然的原创配乐和配音对话中，使世界及其角色栩栩如生。</p>",
